---
title: Quick Pork Schnitzel & Katsu Sauce with Charred Corn Slaw & Japanese Dressing
description: The golden crunch of a crumbed pork schnitzel can never be beaten. Dazzle at the dinner table with two superb
sauces, a dark katsu sauce for the pork and a Japanese dressing to elevate the charred corn slaw to new heights.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
